(Worked Example 2) Tj
T*
(1. Choose a second example that still focuses on verb-form and tense-consistency) Tj
T*
(exercises.) Tj
T*
(2. Break the task into smaller parts and link each part to the rule being used.) Tj
T*
(3. Point out how to avoid shifting tense halfway through a sentence or paragraph while) Tj
T*
(solving it.) Tj
